  "detailed_description": "Explore the small town of ShadeCreek and unravel the many mysteries hidden within.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562270/extras/b242b7f3b12ba3d95118d044a1be7572.avif?t=1655333558\" width=512 height=216 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>An Accidental Hero</u></strong></h2><br>After a Lightning bolt prematurely ends Robo's charging routine, it wakes to find that not all is quite right within the town of ShadeCreek. <br>Use your detective skills to uncover the secrets that the residents are hiding.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Detective Abilities</u></strong></h2>Use your brain to use advanced investigation abilities such as:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Talking to people<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562270/extras/6c3b119418641ddb6a7b4336e9d16976.avif?t=1655333558\" width=512 height=216 /></span><br></li><li> Thinking About What they Said<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562270/extras/49d581a1ff25c9e57a67453e35111518.avif?t=1655333558\" width=512 height=216 /></span><br></li><li> Picking Stuff Up<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562270/extras/9bab1bf4ad4ba8433dd2a066c60fd4bb.avif?t=1655333558\" width=512 height=216 /></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >you Get the Idea.</h2></h2></h2></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Endings</h2><br>Play with the lives of the people living in ShadeCreek by getting the 4 different endings to the game.<br>In this world, robots can't lie (or so they say), so everyone will believe you, for better or worse.",
  "about_the_game": "Explore the small town of ShadeCreek and unravel the many mysteries hidden within.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562270/extras/b242b7f3b12ba3d95118d044a1be7572.avif?t=1655333558\" width=512 height=216 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>An Accidental Hero</u></strong></h2><br>After a Lightning bolt prematurely ends Robo's charging routine, it wakes to find that not all is quite right within the town of ShadeCreek. <br>Use your detective skills to uncover the secrets that the residents are hiding.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Detective Abilities</u></strong></h2>Use your brain to use advanced investigation abilities such as:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Talking to people<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562270/extras/6c3b119418641ddb6a7b4336e9d16976.avif?t=1655333558\" width=512 height=216 /></span><br></li><li> Thinking About What they Said<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562270/extras/49d581a1ff25c9e57a67453e35111518.avif?t=1655333558\" width=512 height=216 /></span><br></li><li> Picking Stuff Up<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562270/extras/9bab1bf4ad4ba8433dd2a066c60fd4bb.avif?t=1655333558\" width=512 height=216 /></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >you Get the Idea.</h2></h2></h2></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Endings</h2><br>Play with the lives of the people living in ShadeCreek by getting the 4 different endings to the game.<br>In this world, robots can't lie (or so they say), so everyone will believe you, for better or worse.",
